oftenstated goal of completing the withdrawal by the end of 1988 
nine years to the month from their invasion the department said 
in a statement 
the soviet withdrawal is indispensable to the ability of the 
afghan people to determine their own future and of the afghan 
refugees to return home in safety and honor it said 
the geneva accords signed last april call for completing the 
