them into the guard or the military dan quayle volunteered 
the indiana senator said wednesday that he didnt know whether 
family connections had been used to get him into the national guard 
and that suggestions that he joined to avoid the draft were a 
cheap shot a day later he said through a spokesman that calls 
may have been made 
the indianapolis news a newspaper owned by quayles family 
